Package: SPINK
Type: Package
Title: SPatial lINKage of RNA and ATAC for spatial multi-ome data
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-03-23
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yue", "Fan", email = "xafanyue@xjtu.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Shiquan", "Sun", email = "sqsunsph@xjtu.edu.cn", role = "aut"))
Description: SPINK is a statistical framework for inferring enhancer-gene 
    regulatory interactions from spatial multi-ome data by explicitly modeling 
    spatial dependence. It provides well-calibrated p-values and powerful 
    detection of true regulatory links compared to existing methods.
